{"tid":845927,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"「網紅」門檻低","createTime":"2018-10-03T04:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T08:00:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee140797d4a44f9ceb36a6847a59bc53011532e3","tid":845927,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20181003/20513002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F20513002&d=Aow8GF3K3lDdrXZekHQXT2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=fb4e00b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F20513002&h=0125da38\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20181003/20513002</a><br />\n<br />\n「網紅」門檻低 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20181003/large/e8804a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20181003%2Flarge%2Fe8804a.jpg&h=1b918562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n所謂「網紅」，十分寬鬆、包容、無監管、欠公信力。它本來是形容詞，指因為偶然機會在網絡上爆紅，成為短暫知名人物者，或透過網絡這個人平台，以各種「表演」、「伎倆」&hellip;&hellip;吸睛吸like吸打賞。「網絡上走紅」？現今不分紅不紅，都自稱或被稱「網紅」，成為一個名詞，身份象徵。<br />\n<br />\n「網紅」太濫了。它又不算KOL（好歹也是Key Opinion Leader，意見領袖），只是流行職業，所以大家見到卓林（小龍女現自行認祖歸宗改姓陳不隨母姓吳）的同性未婚妻Andi是「網紅」；傅恆侍衞的前前前女友大金是「網紅」；得土豪巨額打賞卻被踢爆是裝富卻挪用公款小會計，又是「網紅」。<br />\n<br />\n「網紅」靠打賞已是常規，一般一、二百元人民幣數千元台幣，女主播都愛理不理，金額愈加愈大，送禮過百萬她可賣弄色相陪你唱歌談心或「私人表演」，甚至約炮，某些平台為變相徵友啟事。<br />\n<br />\n直至大家見到，連689也成鍵盤戰士，天天發放（負能量無建樹）仇恨文字，廣交筆友還「約炮」（狂發律師信開炮），企圖東山再起。連被阿爺DQ的下崗人士也不甘寂寞，踴躍加入「網紅」求打賞，可見此行門檻之低。  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n大家都是遊客 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n米芝蓮Ocean憶麻婆炒飯 (鄧達智)"},{"pid":"e28859cf5f915b38083bd4dfb0c71debdbecfda8","tid":845927,"uid":133529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:00:56.000Z","msg":"操逼，給點錢就可以操她們的逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523be65c319edab421b62a3f93b6d33eda281f52","tid":845927,"uid":199179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:41:29.000Z","msg":"網你老母紅"},{"pid":"4a9572ac28287d0d0f86836f050988a048cebc5a","tid":845927,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}